      <title>马斯克生意的成功并不取决于特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/the-success-of-musk-s-business-doesn-t-depend-on-trump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自特朗普当选以来，埃隆·马斯克的商业帝国取得了巨大成功，其中包括 SpaceX。据知情人士透露，这家火箭公司正在商谈出售内部人士股份的交易，交易对这家火箭和卫星制造商的估值约为 3500 亿美元。Max Chafkin 报道（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/the-success-of-musk-s-business-doesn-t-depend-on-trump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:45:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
