      <title>韩国混乱为亚洲公开赛奠定谨慎基调：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈令人震惊地决定实施 40 多年来首次戒严，但数小时后又改变政策，令全球市场措手不及，亚洲股市开盘涨跌互现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国动乱：抗议者冲击国会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/people-confront-security-forces-s-korea-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈宣布戒严数小时后，韩国国会大厦内外的警察和士兵与抗议者发生冲突。士兵准备进入大楼时，抗议者袖手旁观，可以看到一些抗议者在大楼内设置路障。尹锡烈几小时后表示，他将解除戒严令。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/people-confront-security-forces-s-korea-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:13:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
